channel.title: PI - Starting up takes a while
channel.description: My PI server usually starts up in 5 seconds, and it still does. It will say online, listening with port 5555 but then when people can't connect for about 2 minutes. It does this after every restart. How can I fix this? I haven't recently added anything, but I was about to add castle wars.
